      "content": "i get that it's not supposed to be \"ideal\" but i'm not talking about a party or anything. just like a small glass of wine. i've heard that alcohol can actually help the sedative work more effectively so youre not tossing and turning for hours. is there like a safe amount or is it just a total no-go regardless?",
